                <div class="uw-page-element uw-pe uw-pe-text_block" data-page-element="text_block" >
<div class="uw-text-block">
    <p>Welcome to the Department of Statistics! We are an academic department in the <a href="https://ls.wisc.edu/">College of Letters &amp; Science (L&amp;S)</a> and <a href="https://cdis.wisc.edu/">School of Computer, Data, and Information Sciences (CDIS)</a></p>
<p>In the growing field of data analysis, statistics and data science are tools that focus on extracting and analyzing data. Through our undergraduate Statistics major, Data Science major, and Data Science certificate programs, our students will be provided with the foundation, tools, and skills to be prepared to solve real-world problems and make data-informed decisions.</p>
<p>General questions about any of our undergraduate programs, can be directed to <a href="mailto:dscert@stat.wisc.edu">our Recruitment Coordinator</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>            </div>
        
